{
  "stem": "11472.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We started-- the men brought in boards and wood, and-- [SIGHS] we came in in May, which was the beginning of the summer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we brought in some provisions with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not far away from fields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So at night when they had potatoes and they had corn in the fields-- And I have to tell you the ingenuity of the men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They bought from the peasants two stones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they made a mill, so we could make our own flour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We brought in two-- from iron made like a little fondues, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they would bring in wood and cut wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they, they made from wood a gun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the peasants would think we, that they have guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They would go out at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And from far away, if the peasant was in the field, they would carry something on their hands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were very, very brave, because we were underneath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had to go out to bring us provisions, food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One time, my father was on the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He used to have this friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This friend of his was hiding a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't remember the boy's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I forgot it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he's now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was in Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This boy used to help my father bring the provisions to the grotto, to the entrance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the men started to look for a second exit, because we were already afraid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They already-- as soon as we settled, they started to look for another exit in case they discovered this exit Well, we knew one thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "If they come in, they have to come in first with feet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had axes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
